{"tid":2295184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實大家支唔支持馬雲","createTime":"2020-11-21T14:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:00:49.000Z","uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54c242507cf9a26c279c8f1a54420d5041ac00b8","tid":2295184,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:35:12.000Z","msg":"先前我曾經出post反對螞蟻金服上市<br />\n因為理論上覺得馬家同中共同流合污<br />\n但依家形勢似乎中共係螞蟻上市未必攞到好處<br />\n似乎只係馬家同埋一班基金佬食大茶飯<br />\n所以中共叫停佢，怕佢地財產比中共還巨大<br />\n<br />\n其實馬雲咁多年德政係創立左支付寶解決左假錢問題<br />\n淘寶雖然假貨為人所詬病，但係評論系統，收貨再放款系統，係百廢代興時代係大幅解決左支国大量問題<br />\n所以佢一句話支国金融根本無系統完全篤中左中共死穴，中共依家當佢任志強一樣<br />\n中共逼害馬雲，係香港都叫停埋上市，本身都係侵害唔存在既一國兩制<br />\n但如果兩派真係開戰，咁就好睇了<br />\n睇下中共會唔會侵吞晒馬雲既財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaebedb6accac32021282393a6d43450858d17f","tid":2295184,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"可以用馬雲做主角拍解剖外星人"},{"pid":"d7427b8e5ffbc086c80ecc207284c09b1b2243d5","tid":2295184,"uid":381265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"我撐陳雲，都算係支持一半啦"},{"pid":"34b4dd16a72da0525bc10643aad31d5f31e97790","tid":2295184,"uid":34530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"其實講真話嘅大陸人都要撐"},{"pid":"7015a5fb7bf387ab6fddd16fa7b25f7b1eb7ca06","tid":2295184,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7427b8e5ffbc086c80ecc207284c09b1b2243d5","tid":2295184,"uid":381265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"我撐陳雲，都算係支持一半啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7ec67224822ec4babe887c46e50fd70cda65ac","tid":2295184,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"